Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.47,0:00:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shimizu's missing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.26,0:00:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know where he's gone.\NI hope he's all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.76,0:00:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.89,0:00:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.\NYou came back to us okay, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.69,0:00:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I haven't come back--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.94,0:00:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.12,0:00:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so nice to Aiko, Hajime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.54,0:00:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well, she's done a lot for me,\Nso it's the least I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.25,0:00:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yue?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.96,0:00:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sit next to you on the way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.17,0:00:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.47,0:00:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no fair if you get\Nit the whole way, Yue-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.80,0:00:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, why am I in the back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.76,0:01:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out, you useless bunny!\NI'm trying to drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.71,0:02:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, what are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.17,0:03:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're human-locating automatons.\NI call them Ornis.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.51,0:03:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They use a gravity stone to fly\Nand an induction stone to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've got a peering stone inside\Nof them that's connected to my eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.60,0:03:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I can see through them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.81,0:03:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find something already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.65,0:03:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a shield?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.86,0:03:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a bag, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.70,0:03:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks new.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.80,0:03:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.02,0:03:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These tracks were made by\Na large four-legged creature...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.57,0:04:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stories say there's a huge monster\Nlurking beyond these two mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.24,0:04:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But look at the crater left here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense someone nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.94,0:04:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feels like it's human.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.69,0:04:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean someone's alive over here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're somewhere behind that waterfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.45,0:04:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fissuring Wave, Wind Wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.93,0:05:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.44,0:05:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You Will?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, that's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.82,0:05:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Will Cudeta!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.78,0:05:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Hajime Nagumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.40,0:05:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The head of the Fuhren Adventurer's Guild\Nsent me to rescue you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The monsters just didn't stop coming,\Nand they drove us into a corner...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, there was...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.42,0:05:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The black dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.22,0:05:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't deserve this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.39,0:05:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is my worthless behind getting\Nrescued when everyone else had to die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.31,0:05:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so relieved to have survived...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.56,0:06:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.61,0:06:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagumo-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.36,0:06:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with being glad you're alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.28,0:06:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanting to live and being happy about\Nit is only human. Hell, it's necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're completely in the right to feel that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.00,0:06:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.92,0:06:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're worried about the guys\Nwho died, then keep living on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.26,0:06:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drag your feet forward one\Nfoot at a time and live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.35,0:06:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Live on...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.68,0:06:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do that, and one day, you might feel like\Nthere was a reason you survived today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotten pretty late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.36,0:06:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.34,0:07:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.19,0:07:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.28,0:07:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.82,0:07:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mere!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.47,0:07:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's no ordinary monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.73,0:08:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I'll help from behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heavenly Calamity!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.18,0:09:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.89,0:09:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Missed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.18,0:09:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yue!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.45,0:09:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fissuring wave--freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.91,0:09:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We have to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.62,0:09:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.92,0:09:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! Get these guys out of here already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.84,0:09:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.47,0:10:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yue! Focus on protecting everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.97,0:10:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take him out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.39,0:10:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hmm, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.89,0:10:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to die, follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.69,0:10:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we just holding him back?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going after him again...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.11,0:10:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time something's ignored me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm just gonna have to make sure it can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.68,0:10:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever been punched in the gut?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.77,0:10:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd it feel? Hurts, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.79,0:11:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.55,0:12:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.68,0:12:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.78,0:12:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, this thing is tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.91,0:12:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard there were monsters out there\Nthat were tougher than the damn mountains,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.25,0:12:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but how many mountains'\Nworth of strength is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yue, Shea, you guys ever heard of the\Nexpression "kick the dragon in its scaly ass"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.76,0:12:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dragon's only weak point\Nis where it doesn't have scales.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.51,0:12:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say they're so well-defended,\Nwhen they fall asleep, nothing can wake them,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if you attack them in one particular spot,\Nthey'll wake up in a heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it in the ass and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.16,0:13:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My rear! My precious behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, remove it!\NRemove it from my rear, I beseech you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.59,0:13:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're a dragonborn?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed! I am a member of\Nthe esteemed dragonborn race!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.56,0:13:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wild circumstances have led me here,\Nand while I will explain forsooth,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.60,0:13:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must ask you to remove\Nthat object from my behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.98,0:13:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.11,0:13:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.82,0:13:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mana is close to empty!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.32,0:13:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I return to my original form in\Nthis state, it could mean disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.37,0:13:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.99,0:13:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will explain everything, just please,\Nrelieve my behind of that object!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.21,0:14:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have little magic remaining...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.42,0:14:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yue asked you a question!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not force it like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.01,0:14:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is far too much for my rear,\Nfar, far too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.47,0:14:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragonborn are supposedly all dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.94,0:14:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's one doing attacking\Nadventurers out here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, do not twist it around so!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will tell all, just please, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.04,0:14:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was manipulated! I was no more than his tool!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He told me to kill\N"that young man and his companions"!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.96,0:14:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.42,0:14:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I flew from my hidden village to\Ninvestigate the travelers from another world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.81,0:14:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But on my journey to the nearby town,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.64,0:15:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I paused for a rest and\Nenjoyed a nap in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.52,0:15:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I did so in my beastly form,\Nas there were monsters in the vicinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.28,0:15:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During my slumber, that man,\Ndressed in dark robes, appeared before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.16,0:15:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He likely used some kind of mind-control magic\Nto usurp my freedom from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.21,0:15:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His seemed to be an expert at his craft.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.59,0:15:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T'was impossible to resist such a spell\Nwhen it was cast over an entire day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.63,0:15:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were in such a deep sleep that this guy\Nwas able to spend all day casting this spell,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.22,0:15:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you didn't even notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.52,0:15:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.52,0:15:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying that because\Nyou were "under his control,"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you couldn't help killing everyone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.19,0:15:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are we supposed to even know\Nif you're telling the truth right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.24,0:15:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just fabricated that story\Nbecause you don't want us to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear, it is the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.41,0:16:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragonborn are a proud kind;\Nwe do not tarnish our name with lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.54,0:16:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.24,0:16:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think she's lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.63,0:16:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What proof do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragonborn are noble and honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.22,0:16:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She swore on her pride.\NThat is how I know she is not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.47,0:16:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.97,0:16:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what the eyes of a liar look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.85,0:16:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think there is yet someone in this age\Nwho knows of the dragonborn...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.69,0:16:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the last surviving vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three centuries ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was often told to look to the dragonborn\Nas models of royal demeanor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible! News from beyond had informed me\Nthat the vampires had been eradicated,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.37,0:16:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you are a princess of their kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.75,0:16:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter,\Nbecause you still killed them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.96,0:16:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I care not for the wars between our kinds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I did take\Ninnocent lives, that is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.35,0:17:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you order me to atone for my actions,\Nthen I will accept the punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.93,0:17:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only ask that you delay\Nthat punishment a short while,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.40,0:17:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,until that dangerous man\Nand his actions are stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.69,0:17:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is attempting to gather an army of monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.65,0:17:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you give me the chance\Nto prevent a tragedy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.53,0:17:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, I don't care about what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.70,0:17:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've caused more\Nthan enough trouble for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.16,0:17:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it up to me by dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.12,0:17:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Surely you wouldn't end this\Nconversation without answering my question?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.67,0:17:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! I swear to you, I will repent!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.88,0:17:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You going to kill her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.97,0:17:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She started the killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.01,0:17:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's not our enemy.\NShe wasn't in control.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.85,0:17:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't killing her break\Nthat rule that's so important to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.73,0:17:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am terribly sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.57,0:17:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, could you please remove\Nthat hindrance from my rear?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.78,0:17:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.70,0:17:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do not take action,\NI will die, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.45,0:18:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.87,0:18:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just try to imagine the\Nsight of a young woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.29,0:18:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,her behind impaled with a thick, hard rod!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.71,0:18:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I could survive that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.42,0:18:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mana is running out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.21,0:18:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not opposed to this new world\Nto which I have been introduced,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I do not want to die in that manner!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.86,0:18:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the love of all that is good,\Nplease, remove it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.07,0:18:22.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.64,0:18:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Slowly, please!\NI am not yet used to this sensation!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.40,0:18:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So rough!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.19,0:18:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This... This feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.15,0:18:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something is happening, yes,\Nsomething is swelling within me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:45.28,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Yes! Just a little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:46.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You dumb lizard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.76,0:19:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked you to be gentle,\Nyet you showed no mercy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.72,0:19:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never have I experienced this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.18,0:19:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That discomfort in my behind still remains,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.31,0:19:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as does the overwhelming pain\NI feel throughout...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.94,0:19:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew pain was such a sweet sensation...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.11,0:19:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.70,0:19:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My sincerest apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.99,0:19:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Tio Klarus,\Na member of the Klarus clan of dragonborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.37,0:19:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This army of monsters is marching on Ur?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.79,0:19:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. The dark-robed man intends\Nto use them to attack the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that army numbers\Nwell into the thousands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.09,0:19:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is more than thousands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.02,0:19:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting five... no, 60,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.85,0:19:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they're already on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.57,0:19:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This far out, it'll take them\Ntwo days to reach the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.11,0:20:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We have to warn them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.45,0:20:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll evacuate everyone,\Nthen call for help, then--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.45,0:20:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could my lord Hajime\Ndo something about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.87,0:20:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Look. My job was to\Nget you back to Fuhren safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.34,0:20:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How am I supposed to fight\Na war while keeping you safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.63,0:20:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nagumo-{\i1}kun{\i0}? Did you get a look\Nat this robed man he was talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.22,0:20:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. I've been checking the ranks of\Nthis army and haven't seen anything like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.31,0:20:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.93,0:20:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you look a bit more?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.31,0:20:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.40,0:20:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.90,0:20:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagumo-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.28,0:20:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just said my only job\Nwas getting Will out safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.03,0:20:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of you can stay here if you want,\Nbut who's gonna go tell the town?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.24,0:20:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.12,0:20:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is just as he says!\NInforming the town should be our top priority!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.29,0:21:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, given a day,\NI will surely recover to full health!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.01,0:21:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.68,0:21:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, my mana reserves\Nare so dry, I can barely move.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.93,0:21:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look at me like\NI am the embodiment of filth!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.23,0:21:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gulp.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should've killed you after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.73,0:21:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your words pierce my heart,\Nyour fist strikes at my very core,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.69,0:21:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and your attacks violate\Nonly my most lewd of areas!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.11,0:21:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart, body, and\Nsoul fill with such pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.75,0:21:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What horrid treatment!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.05,0:21:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such new sensations!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.77,0:21:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.44,0:22:05.15,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"Good morning," "Good night,"\Nall those simple things
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.15,0:22:10.24,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,are so dreamlike and beloved to me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.24,0:22:14.95,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I finally met you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.95,0:22:21.59,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is so special, thank you again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.34,0:22:29.72,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think I'd be lonely all by myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.72,0:22:34.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,That is, until you found me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.93,0:22:40.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.52,0:22:45.94,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,That is, until I thought of a world without you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.94,0:22:52.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you believe it?\NI miss you, I'm so fond of you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.78,0:22:58.58,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, don't forget it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.58,0:23:03.67,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Shine bright like the first star in the night
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.67,0:23:09.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and stay closer to me than anyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.47,0:23:14.85,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never let you go
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.85,0:23:20.35,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never let go of that hand
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.35,0:23:27.90,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay by my side and shine
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ARIFURETA: From Commonplace\Nto World's Strongest.